dcterms:creator: A. Krizhevsky
I. Sutskever
G. E. Hinton
dcterms:description: Cifar10 dataset contains RGB 32x32 images of 10 classes (airplane, automobile, bird, cat, deer, dog, frog, horse, ship, truck). The total number of images is 60,000 with 6,000 images for each class.
dcterms:title: Cifar10

dcterms:creator: P. Helber
B. Bischke
A. Dengel
D. Borth
dcterms:description: Eurosat dataset contains Sentinel-2 satellite images covering both 13 spectral bands and RGB (3-channel) 64x64 images and consisting of 10 classes (AnnualCrop, Forest, HerbaceousVegetation, Highway, Industrial, Pasture, PermanentCrop, Residential, River, SeaLake) with in total 27,000 labeled and geo-referenced images.
dcterms:title: Eurosat (rgb)

dcterms:creator: H. H. Aghdam
E. J. Heravi
D. Puig
dcterms:description: The UCmerced land-use dataset contains 256x256 RGB satellite images of 21 classes of land use, with 100 images for each class.
dcterms:title: UCmerced land use
